This place has amazing food and I always get the Chloe's favorite! I would rate this place a 5 stars if it wasn't for the poor customer service at the registers. There seems to always be the same gal up front who never smiles and is reluctant to answer any questions regarding the menu. I hate to downgrade from a 5-4; owner is extremely nice and is always there to help and my experience great.

